raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"main_street\")
do social_post(\"mabel_shopping_spree\")
Mabel: I just finished class!
Mabel: On my way to the stores 🥰
Mabel: img: mabel/135
Player: Hey, still in class
Mabel: And you're texting me?? 😠
Mabel: You're so naughty 🤭
- You're the one texting me
	Player: You're the one texting me
	Player: You are the criminal here 😏
	Mabel: Am not!
- Wanna find out how naughty I can be tonight?
	Player: Wanna find out how naughty I can be tonight?
	Mabel: I'll bite you if you do anything crazy 😺 Rawr
Mabel: Okay I'll talk to you later then! 🤪
do advance_time(0, 52)
do Story.set_location(\"shopping_mall\")
Mabel: img: mabel/136
Mabel: I remember you used to love eating these
Player: They're great haha
Player: Where did you find those?
Mabel: Agency secrets
Player: 😄
Mabel: 🕵️‍♀️
do advance_time(0, 26)
do Story.set_location(\"shopping_mall\")
Mabel: img: mabel/137
Mabel: Oh uhm.. did you wanna try something like this? 🙈
Mabel: Only if you want to
Mabel: I wouldn't by myself
- We can try it!
	set Story.flag = \"AlcoholAcquired\"
	Player: We can try it!
	Mabel: Sure thing 😀
- Lets hold off on that
	Player: Lets hold off on that
	Mabel: Oki dokes 😊
if Story.has_flag(\"LingerieRequest\"):
	do advance_time(0, 56)
	Mabel: Uhm babe?
	Player: Yeah?
	Mabel: I wanted to erm..
	Mabel: Remember last night you said the thing?
	Player: What thing babe 😂
	Mabel: The sexy PJ thing 👀
	Mabel: Well I just wanted to try one on.. I'm not planning to wear it but I got a little curious
	Mabel: Do you think it looks nice on me?
	Mabel: img: mabel/138
	- Wow 😳
		Player: Wow 😳
	- Amazing 😍
		Player: Amazing 😍
	Mabel: Seriously? 🥰
	Mabel: Okay, I'm NOT wearing this tonight cause.. shy 👉👈
	Mabel: But I didn't want you to feel like I don't care about what you think
	Mabel: 🙆‍♀️
	Player: I appreciate it 😍
	Mabel: Love you 🥰
	Player: Love you too 🥰
	Mabel: Gotta run before they think I'm trying to steal it omg 😭
	Player: You're a spy and a thief 🤣
	Mabel: 😭
=> END"
